		background-size: 0.25rem;
		background-repeat: repeat;
		background-position: bottom;
		backdrop-filter: blur(0.5rem) brightness(20%);

		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: -1;
	}

	#bg {
	}
</style>
